Package: sdcard-formatter
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, policykit-1
Maintainer: SD Card Formatter Team <support@example.com>
Description: SD Card Formatter GUI (format_sd not included)
 GTK3 GUI for formatting SD cards and USB drives using the official
 Tuxera format_sd binary. On first run, you will be prompted to download
 and select the format_sd binary from the official SD Association website.
 Supports Quick, Discard, and Overwrite modes.
